ik allies with Bhaisaab, but those in the shadows threaten to destroy the very game they seek to control.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraphindia.com/entertainment/team-inside-edge-on-the-charm-and-challenge-of-season-2/cid/1725740|title=Team \u2018Inside Edge\u2019 on the charm and challenge of season 2.|accessdate=10 December 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Episodes===\n{{Episode table |background=#0257AC |overall=  |title= |writer= |director=[[Karan Anshuman]] |airdate=06 December 2019 |episodes=\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 1\n |Title = Run Up\n |DirectedBy = Aakash Bhatia\n |WrittenBy = Karan Anshuman\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2019|12|6}}\n |ShortSummary = \n |LineColor = 0257AC\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 2\n |Title = Paddle Sweep\n |DirectedBy = Aakash Bhatia\n |WrittenBy = Karan Anshuman\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2019|12|6}}\n |ShortSummary = \n |LineColor = 0257AC\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 3\n |Title = Hawk-Eye\n |DirectedBy = Aakash Bhatia\n |WrittenBy = Karan Anshuman\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2019|12|6}}\n |ShortSummary = \n |LineColor = 0257AC\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 4\n |Title = Doctored\n |DirectedBy = Karan Anshuman, Gurmmeet Singh\n |WrittenBy = Karan Anshuman\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2019|12|6}}\n |ShortSummary = \n |LineColor = 0257AC\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 5\n |Title = Block Hole\n |DirectedBy = Aakash Bhatia\n |WrittenBy = Karan Anshuman\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2019|12|6}}\n |ShortSummary = \n |LineColor = 0257AC\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 6\n |Title = Turn\n |DirectedBy = Aakash Bhatia\n |WrittenBy = Karan Anshuman\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2019|12|6}}\n |ShortSummary = \n |LineColor = 0257AC\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 7\n |Title = Yo Yo\n |DirectedBy = Karan Anshuman, Gurmmeet Singh\n |WrittenBy = Karan Anshuman\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2019|12|6}}\n |ShortSu